\newlabel{tab:results_sparse}{{IV}{13}{3D quadrotor navigation at a lower obstacle count ($N_{\mathrm {obs}}=50$), averaged over $17$ seeds ($\alpha =0.10$); same setup and columns as Table~\ref {tab:pybullet_results}. Reporting both densities shows how each method behaves as the workspace becomes less cluttered}{table.4}{}}
